CHANGELOG
=========

MISTY-NET VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
------------------------------------

Added:
- `MistyCodec` for frame-based communication using `LengthDelimitedCodec` and MessagePack.
- `Frame`, `HeadFrame`, `TailFrame` definitions for the Misty protocol.
- `Status` enum for protocol-level status codes.
- `Router` for dispatching service calls.
- `MistyService` trait for implementing networked services.
- `NetError` for unified network error handling.

Changed:
- Added dependencies: `quinn`, `tokio-util`, `rmp-serde`, `async-trait`, `bytes`, `serde`.

MISTY-CODEGEN-RS VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
------------------------------------------

Added:
- Code generation for schemas and enums.

MISTY-CORE VERSION 0.0.3 (2026-01-22)
------------------------------------

Added:
- `CodeGenerator` trait for unified code generation interface.

Changed:
- Added dependency on `misty-parser`.

MISTY-PARSER VERSION 0.0.3 (2026-01-22)
--------------------------------------

Added:
- Validator module Workspace struct.
- Full workspace validator implementation.

Changed:
- Added crate scoping to the public uses of the AST parsers.

MISTY-PARSER VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
--------------------------------------

Added:
- Pest parser and grammar for Misty.
- All AST node parsers.

MISTY-CORE VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
------------------------------------

Added:
- Basic error shells.

Changed:
- Refactored to remove errors for improved flexibility.

MISTY-AST VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
-----------------------------------

Added:
- File AST node.
- Full AST definition for the Misty language.

VERSION 0.0.1 (2026-01-21)
--------------------------

Added:
- Initial workspace scaffolding and crate layout.